  "text": "JET [CITATION_1] allows analysing the dependencies between VCS versions. The authors extend the Ring meta-model [CITATION_2] to perform the computations. Epicea uses Ring as well. It would be interesting to apply JET dependency analysis to logs to get fine-grained results.",
